{
  "stem": "18770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 53.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do know that what happened was that when the war was coming, we were in a situation of, first of all-- I mean, I'm not saying 'we' because my sister and I were way too young to have any political sense, but the adults in the family.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was definitely a sense that war, you know, that war was imminent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at the same time, there was that belief that it could not happen because England would not-- was-- had a, had a some kind of a pact with Poland.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That if Poland was invaded, England would go to war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the belief was, there was no way that Germany would risk starting a war with England in order to attack Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the general belief.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was one aspect of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think what happened-- and this again, I'm sort of piecing together from what I've heard and-- but basically, it was something like this.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The family-- or the bulk of the family-- was on vacation-- another one of those many vacations-- when-- in fact, Zakopane, the place I mentioned before where the skiing, except this was summer or spring.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could also go to a beautiful place in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were there on vacation and the war began.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- we, we got information or letters or communications-- I don't know how that worked-- that it would be advisable not to go back to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That it was dangerous to go back there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One thing that happened was that as soon as the Germans came into Poland-- to that part of Poland-- there was a reward out for my grandfather because he represented one of the several dozen very prominent, wealthy Jews that they wanted to get their hands on.",
      "word_count": 47
    }
  ],
